OL,5, Publishing giant Simon & Schuster is to
OL,6, be sold to a private equity giant for  
OL,7, $1.6bn (#1.27bn) in cash.              
OL,9,FThe deal with investor KKR marks the   
OL,10,Flikely end of a years-long saga for    
OL,11,Fowner Paramount Global, which had been 
OL,12,Flooking for a buyer for the book       
OL,13,Fcompany since 2020.                    
OL,15,FCompetition concerns had scuppered a   
OL,16,Fprevious deal, which valued the firm at
OL,17,Fmore than $2bn.                        
OL,19,FKKR said the publisher would continue  
OL,20,Fto operate independently.              
